**Phase 3: Outline Modal**

Wire up outline modal interactions: live preview on selection change, confirm jump, cancel restore.

**Background:**
Outline modal shows live preview: as user moves selection (j/k), background viewport scrolls to preview that heading without committing. Enter confirms, Esc cancels and restores origin.

**Preview Behavior:**
- On selection change: update viewport.top_line to show selected heading
- Do NOT update viewport.cursor_line yet (preview only)
- Background document view updates in real-time
- User sees heading context before committing

**Confirm (Enter):**
- Set cursor to selected heading line
- Recenter viewport
- Close modal (is_open = false)
- Clear origin state
- Show status: "Jumped to: [heading title]"

**Cancel (Esc):**
- Restore viewport.cursor_line to origin_line
- Restore viewport.top_line to origin_top_line
- Close modal
- Discard all preview changes
- Show status: "Cancelled"

**Implementation:**
```rust
pub enum OutlineIntent {
    Open,
    FilterInput(char),
    FilterBackspace,
    MoveUp,
    MoveDown,
    Confirm,
    Cancel,
}

pub fn handle_outline_intent(model: &mut Model, intent: OutlineIntent) -> Cmd {
    match intent {
        OutlineIntent::Open => {
            model.outline.open(model.viewport.cursor_line, model.viewport.top_line);
            preselect_current_heading(&mut model);
        }
        OutlineIntent::MoveUp | OutlineIntent::MoveDown => {
            model.outline.move_selection(intent);
            apply_live_preview(&mut model);  // Update viewport for preview
        }
        OutlineIntent::Confirm => {
            let target_line = model.outline.selected_heading_line();
            model.viewport.cursor_line = target_line;
            model.viewport.recenter(target_line);
            model.outline.close();
            set_status("Jumped to heading");
        }
        OutlineIntent::Cancel => {
            model.viewport.cursor_line = model.outline.origin_line;
            model.viewport.top_line = model.outline.origin_top_line;
            model.outline.close();
            set_status("Cancelled");
        }
    }
}
```

**Edge Cases:**
- Filter to zero results, no selection to confirm
- Selection out of bounds after filter change
- Rapid selection changes (preview must keep up)
- Confirm with no headings selected

**Testing:**
- Open outline, move selection, verify preview updates
- Confirm jump and verify cursor moved
- Cancel and verify origin restored
- Test filter -> select -> confirm flow
- Test rapid selection changes
- Manual QA: preview feels responsive

**Acceptance:**
- Live preview works (background viewport updates)
- Confirm commits to selected heading
- Cancel restores original position
- Edge cases handled gracefully
- Tests pass for all interactions
